Package: nifffty
Title: Post Events to 'IFTTT' 'Maker' Channels and Receive 'Maker' Events
Version: 0.1.1.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Bob", "Rudis", email = "bob@rud.is", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Bob", "Connelly", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Bob Rudis <bob@rudis.net>
Description: Provides a simple interface to post messages to 'IFTTT' 'Maker'
    channels from R, enabling R scripts to trigger 'IFTTT' recipes with optional data
    payloads and also receive and process Maker web requests.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    testthat
Imports:
    httr,
    Rook,
    httpuv,
    jsonlite,
    methods,
    tools
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
